sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Frontend (React)
    participant Backend (Node.js)
    participant SerialPort
    participant Database (SQLite)

    User->>Frontend: 1. Click "Open Port COM3"
    Frontend->>Backend: 2. WebSocket: { "port": "COM3" }
    Backend->>SerialPort: 3. serialHelper.open("COM3")
    activate SerialPort

    loop Data Acquisition
        SerialPort-->>Backend: 4. Raw Buffer Frame
        Backend->>Backend: 5. dataProcessor.process(buffer)
        Note right of Backend: - Line Mapping<br/>- Zero Calibration<br/>- Smoothing
        Backend->>Frontend: 6. WebSocket: { type: "pressure_data", payload: { matrix, stats } }
        Frontend->>Frontend: 7. usePressureData.updateFromMatrix()
        Note left of Frontend: Re-render Heatmap & 3D Model

        alt Recording Active
            Backend->>Database: 8. dbHelper.insertFrame()
            activate Database
            Database-->>Backend: 9. Success
            deactivate Database
        end
    end
    deactivate SerialPort

    User->>Frontend: 10. Click "Download CSV"
    Frontend->>Backend: 11. WebSocket: { "download": "2026-03-01" }
    Backend->>Database: 12. dbHelper.queryFramesByDate()
    activate Database
    Database-->>Backend: 13. Return Frames
    deactivate Database
    Backend->>Backend: 14. csvHelper.exportFramesToCsv()
    Backend->>Frontend: 15. WebSocket: { type: "download_ready", payload: { path } }
